data.description: FABULOUS townhome awaits its new owner. The main level includes a large living and dining area and a beautiful kitchen. The kitchen offers granite counters, lovely cabinets, with an island perfect for entertaining. The second level offers three bedrooms and two full baths which includes a large primary suite with a walk-in closet. Enjoy the privacy and entertainment space of the back patio. This home is just a few minutes from shopping, medical facilities, and many other necessary amenities. Do not miss the chance to call this one your own!  Washer, dryer and refrigerator remain.
